		<Container classes="space-y-10 lg:space-y-24">
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="label">Atlas Broncos</div>
				<h2 class="text-balance max-w-[16em]">Where passion meets decades of experience</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-12">
				<div class="space-y-6 col-span-6 lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="h6">Why Choose Atlas?</div>
						<div class="font-light space-y-4">
							<p>When you choose Atlas Broncos, you're not just getting a restored Broncoâ€”you're getting a vehicle built with passion, expertise, and an uncompromising attention to detail.</p>
							<p>We take pride in every Bronco we restore, ensuring that it's not only visually stunning but also built to perform at the highest level, whether you're cruising on the highway or exploring rugged trails.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<ButtonLink>Contact Us</ButtonLink>
				</div>

				<div class="w-full h-full col-span-6 lg:col-span-4">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-6 gap-6 h-full">
						{
							items.map((i, n) => (
								<Image
									pictureClass={["h-full w-full lg:col-span-2", n == 0 ? "col-span-6" : "col-span-3"]}
									class="rounded-2xl h-full w-full object-cover shadow-2xl"
									src={i}
									sizes={n == 0 ? "(min-width: 1024px) 350px, 100vw" : "(min-width: 1024px) 350px, 50vw"}
								/>
							))
						}
					</div>
				</div>
